I"2<p>The contact part of the index page is consisted of two elements:</p>

<ol>
  <li>Text</li>
  <li>Your email address</li>
</ol>

<p>You can modify the Contact text from the /contact.html file and set the email in the site config:</p>

<pre><code data-trim="" class="yaml">
email: "your@email.here"
</code></pre>

<p>Donâ€™t be afraid of email harvesting, write your email properly and the page will perform javascript obfuscation.</p>

